iated with acquisitions.</p></td></tr><tr><td class="bwpadl0 bwpadr0 bwpadb3 bwvertalignt" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin bwalignl"><sup>(2)</sup></p></td><td class="bwvertalignt bwpadl1" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin bwalignl">EBITDA is a non-GAAP measure used by management to evaluate the Company's ongoing operations. EBITDA is defined as operating profit plus certain adjustments, such as non-recurring cost reduction actions, fees and non-cash inventory charges associated with acquisitions, plus depreciation and amortization.</p></td></tr></table><table cellspacing="0" class="bwtablemarginb bwblockalignl bwwidth100"><tr><td class="bwpadl0" colspan="8" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin"></p><p class="bwcellpmargin bwalignc"><span class="bwuline">NORDSON CORPORATION</span></p><p class="bwcellpmargin bwalignc">RECONCILIATION OF NON-GAAP MEASURES - ADJUSTED NET INCOME AND EARNINGS PER SHARE (Unaudited)</p><p class="bwcellpmargin bwalignc">(Dollars in thousands)</p><p class="bwcellpmargin"></p></td></tr><tr><td class="bwvertalignb bwpadl0 bwwidth63" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin"></p></td><td class="bwvertalignb bwsinglebottom bwpadl0" colspan="7" rowspan="1"><p class="bwalignc bwcellpmargin">Three Months Ended</p></td></tr><tr><td class="bwvertalignb bwpadl0 bwwidth63" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin"></p></td><td class="bwvertalignb bwsinglebottom bwpadl0" colspan="3" rowspan="1"><p class="bwalignc bwcellpmargin">January 31, 2026</p></td><td class="bwvertalignb bwpadl0 bwwidth1" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin"></p></td><td class="bwvertalignb bwsinglebottom bwpadl0" colspan="3" rowspan="1"><p class="bwalignc bwcellpmargin">January 31, 2025</p></td></tr><tr><td class="bwvertalignb bwpadl0 bwwidth63" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin"><b><span class="bwuline">GAAP AS REPORTED</span></b></p></td><td class="bwvertalignb bwpadl0" colspan="3" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpm