 colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin bwalignl">Adjusted net income is a non-GAAP measure defined as net income plus tax effected adjustments and other discrete tax items.</p></td></tr><tr><td class="bwpadl0 bwpadr0 bwpadb3 bwvertalignt" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin bwalignl"><sup>(4)</sup></p></td><td class="bwvertalignt bwpadl1" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin bwalignl">Adjusted earnings per share is a non-GAAP measure defined as GAAP EPS adjusted for tax effected adjustments and other discrete tax items.</p></td></tr></table><table cellspacing="0" class="bwtablemarginb bwblockalignl bwwidth100"><tr><td class="bwpadl0" colspan="8" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin"></p><p class="bwcellpmargin bwalignc"><span class="bwuline">NORDSON CORPORATION</span></p><p class="bwcellpmargin bwalignc">RECONCILIATION OF NON-GAAP MEASURES - OPERATING CASH FLOW TO FREE CASH FLOW (Unaudited)</p><p class="bwcellpmargin bwalignc">(Dollars in thousands)</p><p class="bwcellpmargin"></p></td></tr><tr><td class="bwvertalignb bwpadl0 bwwidth63" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin"></p></td><td class="bwvertalignb bwpadl0 bwsinglebottom" colspan="7" rowspan="1"><p class="bwalignc bwcellpmargin">Year to Date</p></td></tr><tr><td class="bwvertalignb bwpadl0 bwwidth63" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin"></p></td><td class="bwvertalignb bwsinglebottom bwpadl0" colspan="3" rowspan="1"><p class="bwalignc bwcellpmargin">January 31, 2026</p></td><td class="bwvertalignb bwpadl0 bwwidth1" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin"></p></td><td class="bwvertalignb bwsinglebottom bwpadl0" colspan="3" rowspan="1"><p class="bwalignc bwcellpmargin">January 31, 2025</p></td></tr><tr><td class="bwvertalignb bwrowaltcolor0 bwpadl0 bwwidth63" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin">Net cash provided by operating activities</p></td><td class="bwvertalignb bwrowaltcolor0 bwpadl0 bwpadr0 bwalignr bwwidth1" colspan="1" rowspa